title: Rocksmith 2014 700 Customs including all officially released DLC
description:
As the title suggest this collection has every single officially released DLC up to and including the Aerosmith pack which was just released on 01/07/2014 and it includes over 750 Custom songs that were created by members of smithyanvil. I have done this as a special request since I do not play on a mac and therefore cannot test these. I do not take credit for these customs as I am not the maker of any of them. I am simply making them available to people so that they don't have to download every single song on their own(Very time consuming process). As always these customs come from the folks over at smithyanvil forums so all credit goes to the people over there. All songs have had their appID's changed to cherub rock so you must own that song in order to play these customs. 

Install instructions

Unrar file
copy contents ~/Library/Application Support/Steam/SteamApps/common/Rocksmith2014/dlc/" ,

You might need to use "Command-Shift-G" to go inside ~/Library since it's hidden by default in the finder;


Once again I do not play on a mac so I do not know if these work or not.
